Curator's comments: Joins with 10664-6; same manuscript. To be studied by Andreas Winkler. Register of administrative documents, including contracts. Demotic text recto and verso. Register of administrative documents, including contracts. Same text as EA 10664-5: these are accounts of the inhabitants of Tebtunis which can be dated to regnal year 35 of either Ptolemy the VIII or IX being a list of houses in the different neighbourhoods of the town (Winkler, pers. comm).
